## 🧠 Why Fork Instead of Clone?

| Fork | Clone |
|------|-------|
| Creates a copy on the Git server | Creates a copy on your local machine |
| Used for collaboration | Used for development |
| Enables Pull Requests | Doesn't create a remote repository |
| Maintains relationship with original repository | Independent local copy |

